<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Mon, 07 Feb 2022 06:37:52 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>外媒：MacBook Pro 續航力表現最好　比 Windwos 筆電長 40% 使用時間</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/07/mbppc/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=mbppc</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 07 Feb 2022 06:37:06 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[macbook pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[電池續航力]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1084919</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>有測試指出，MacBook Pro 16 的電池續航力比 Windows 中高階款筆電好，長達 1195 分鐘 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>有測試指出，MacBook Pro 16 的電池續航力比 Windows 中高階款筆電好，長達 1195 分鐘，遠超第二名 Dell G5 5515 的 746 分鐘。</p><p>外國知名科技評測專家 Jarrod’sTech 於 YouTube 上載了一條 MacBook Pro 16 的評測影片，將 MacBook Pro 16 的電池續航力、擴充性、跑分等性能與 20 多款 Windows 中高階手提電腦比較。</p><p>Jarrod’sTech 用作測試的 MacBook Pro 16 配備 M1 Pro 晶片，搭載 10 核心 CPU 及 16 核心 GPU，而配備 M1 Max 晶片的 MacBook Pro 16 GPU 則為 32 核心。因此兩款的 MacBook Pro 16 表現會有出入，M1 Pro 的電池續航力會略勝一籌。</p><p>測試結果顯示，MacBook Pro 16 的電池續航力在一眾 Windows 機中跑出，長達 1195 分鐘，即約 19.9 小時。而續航力僅次於 MacBook Pro 16 的 Dell G5 5515，配備 Ryzen 5800H 處理器與 3060 GPU，表現為 746 分鐘，即約 12.4 小時；即 MacBook Pro 16 比 Dell G5 5515 多約 40% 使用時間，但玩遊戲 The Witcher 3 的續航力僅約 2 小時。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644204899-1055d045cf64bd6869afcef496b5351c.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084921" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644204899-1055d045cf64bd6869afcef496b5351c-694x367.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="367" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644204899-1055d045cf64bd6869afcef496b5351c-694x367.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644204899-1055d045cf64bd6869afcef496b5351c-768x406.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644204899-1055d045cf64bd6869afcef496b5351c.jpeg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>而在 Cinebench R23 的電池模式上，MSI GE76 Raider 12UHS 及 ASUS Strix G15 Advantage 的電池續航力分別奪得首兩名，而 MacBook Pro 16 僅屈居第三。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205680-aca31950a2a5bbf3ccb1382370db8690.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205680-aca31950a2a5bbf3ccb1382370db8690-694x388.png" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205680-aca31950a2a5bbf3ccb1382370db8690-694x388.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205680-aca31950a2a5bbf3ccb1382370db8690-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205680-aca31950a2a5bbf3ccb1382370db8690.png 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>雖然 MacBook Pro 16 的電池續航力表現出色，但其他範疇卻不如 Windows 機款，Wi-Fi 速度竟排最尾，慢第一名的 Gigabyte Aero 17 YD 一倍多；遊戲方面的排名亦倒數第三；後續升級性則表現最差，僅 0.5。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205792-fcf98d157f6808b12a32b467f14db4db.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084923" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205792-fcf98d157f6808b12a32b467f14db4db-694x391.png" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205792-fcf98d157f6808b12a32b467f14db4db-694x391.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205792-fcf98d157f6808b12a32b467f14db4db-768x433.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205792-fcf98d157f6808b12a32b467f14db4db.png 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205922-3d76aebc071b9225473559968b3d464d.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205922-3d76aebc071b9225473559968b3d464d-694x389.png" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205922-3d76aebc071b9225473559968b3d464d-694x389.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205922-3d76aebc071b9225473559968b3d464d-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205922-3d76aebc071b9225473559968b3d464d.png 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205980-883cce1247295ab2a586669d3f2c9dac.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084925" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205980-883cce1247295ab2a586669d3f2c9dac-694x393.png" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205980-883cce1247295ab2a586669d3f2c9dac-694x393.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1644205980-883cce12